 PiRC System Architecture

End-to-End Economic Infrastructure for Pi Network

---

 1. Architectural Vision

PiRC is designed as a modular, scalable, and adaptive economic infrastructure that transforms Pi Network into a self-regulating digital economy.

---

«It is not a single system.»

«It is a layered architecture coordinating value, behavior, and liquidity across the entire ecosystem.»

